The paper deals with image segmentation and scene parsing using deep neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of recurrent FCNs and deeply supervised learning suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The incorporation of level set methods and sub-pixel accuracy may also indicate a connection to numerical analysis (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
